  "title": "Sales Executive (Basic $2,800 – $3,500 / Jurong East)",
  "description": "<p>Position: Sales Executive (ID6049)<br />Location: Jurong East<br />Working Hours: Mon to Fri: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM , Sat: 8:30 AM – 12:30 PM<br /><br />Salary Range:<br />• Basic Salary: $2,800 – $3,500 (depending on experience)<br />• Attractive Commission Scheme (will be disclosed when interview)<br />• Transport allowance provided<br /><br />Job Responsibilities:<br />• Develop and maintain strong relationships with new and existing clients<br />• Understand customer needs and provide suitable machinery or engineering solutions<br />• Prepare quotations, proposals, and sales reports<br />• Coordinate with the technical team to meet customer requirements<br />• Follow up on after-sales service to ensure client satisfaction<br />• Meet sales targets and contribute to the company's revenue growth<br /><br />Requirements:<br />• Minimum 1-2 years of sales experience, preferably in machinery, engineering, or industrial equipment<br />• Strong communication and negotiation skills<br />• Proactive, self-motivated, and result-oriented<br />• Class 3 driving license with own vehicle preferred (for client visits)</p>",
